#1 Summary: Valid login to the application

Steps:
1. Go to http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login
2. Enter valid login into 'email' field
3. Enter valid password into 'password' field
4. Click 'Вход' button

Expected result: Displays avatar and username in the top right corner
-----------------------------------------------

#2 Summary: User logs out from the application

Steps:
1. Go to http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login
2. Enter valid login into 'email' field
3. Enter valid password into 'password' field
4. Click 'Вход' button
5. Click on avatar in the top right corner
6. Click 'Выход' button on the flyout

Expected result: Displays 'Авторизация' on the login box
-----------------------------------------------

#3 Summary: Create new deal

Steps:
1. Go to http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login
2. Enter valid login into 'email' field
3. Enter valid password into 'password' field
4. Click 'Вход' button
5. Go to 'Сделки' on the left panel
7. Click '+'(Add) button
8. Select values from 'Deal date' drop-down list: date, month, year, hours, minutes
9. Select value from 'Тип сделки' drop-down list
10. Select value from 'Покупатель' drop-down list
11. Select value from 'Поставщик' drop-down list
12. Click 'Создать' button

Expected result: Displays Deals landing page with created deal in the list
-----------------------------------------------

#4 Summary: Create new installation

Steps:
1. Go to http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login
2. Enter valid login into 'email' field
3. Enter valid password into 'password' field
4. Click 'Вход' button
5. Go to 'Установка' on the left panel
6. Click '+'(Add) button
7. Select value from 'Installation date' drop-down lists: date, month, year, hours, minutes
8. Select value from 'Аппарат' drop-down list
9. Select value from 'Сотрудник' drop-down list
10. Click 'Создать' button

Expected result: Displays Installation landing page with created installation
-----------------------------------------------

#5 Summary: Create new service

Steps:
1. Go to http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login
2. Enter valid login into 'email' field
3. Enter valid password into 'password' field
4. Click 'Вход' button
5. Go to 'Обслуживание' on the left panel
6. Click '+'(Add) button
7. Fill up fields: 'Service changes', 'Service operations'
8. Select value from 'Service date' drop-down lists: date, month, year, hours, minutes
9. Select value from 'Аппарат' drop-down list
10. Select value from 'Сотрудник' drop-down list
11. Click 'Создать' button

Expected result: Displays Service landing page with created service